cardboard sheets (4 mm thickness);
rulers (school size (0.3 m) and long (0.5...1 m));
pencil;
paper knife;
awl;
scissors;
cardboard bender;
PC, printer and 5 A4 sheets to print base drawings.

- cardboard sheet (900x260 mm, t=2 mm, two layers);
